<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>OKKI 看板 — 方案对比</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 24px; color: #333; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2em; margin: 24px 0 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .badge { font-size: 0.7em; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: normal; }
  .badge-a { background: #e3f2fd; color: #1565c0; }
  .badge-b { background: #fff3e0; color: #e65100; }

  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08); font-size: 0.88em; }
  th { background: #fafafa; padding: 10px 10px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.82em; color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  td { padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; vertical-align: top; }
  tr:hover td { background: #fafbfc; }
  .section-row td { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 6px 10px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8; }
  .section-row:hover td { background: #f5f5f5; }

  .driver-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.78em; margin: 1px 2px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .driver-red { background: #ffebee; color: #c62828; border: 1px solid #ffcdd2; }
  .driver-yellow { background: #fff8e1; color: #e65100; border: 1px solid #ffecb3; }
  .driver-none { color: #bbb; font-size: 0.82em; }

  .name-col { font-weight: 500; min-width: 100px; }
  .stage-col { font-size: 0.82em; }

  .priority-dot { display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 6px; }
  .dot-red { background: #d32f2f; }
  .dot-yellow { background: #f57c00; }

  .compare-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .panel { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
  .panel h3 { font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0; }

  .diff-note { margin-top: 16px; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.82em; }
  .diff-pro { background: #e8f5e9; color: #2e7d32; border-left: 3px solid #4caf50; }
  .diff-con { background: #fbe9e7; color: #bf360c; border-left: 3px solid #ff7043; }

  .interaction-hint { margin-top: 12px; font-size: 0.78em; color: #999; text-align: center; }
  .action-col { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; max-width: 200px; }

  hr { border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 32px 0; }
  .verdict { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
  .verdict h3 { font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .verdict ul { margin-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h2>方案 A：客户聚合式 <span class="badge badge-a">一个客户一行 · 驱动因子叠标签</span></h2>

<table>
